com.revolsys.beans

Class RunnableCallable<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.revolsys.parallel.AbstractRunnable
      • com.revolsys.beans.RunnableCallable<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the result.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable

    public class RunnableCallable<T>
extends AbstractRunnable

    A Runnable wrapper for a Callable. The result of the Callable can be obtained using the getResult() method.

    NOTE: This class is designed to be used for a single invocation only.
